<item>
            <title>[LU-18794] kernel update [RHEL 9.5 5.14.0-503.31.1.el9_5]</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-18794</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Security Fix(es):&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;kernel: ACPI: extlog: fix NULL pointer dereference check (CVE-2023-52605)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;kernel: vsock/virtio: Initialization of the dangling pointer occurring in vsk-&amp;gt;trans (CVE-2024-50264)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;kernel: HID: core: zero-initialize the report buffer (CVE-2024-50302)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;kernel: can: bcm: Fix UAF in bcm_proc_show() (CVE-2023-52922)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;kernel: mm: fix NULL pointer dereference in alloc_pages_bulk_noprof (CVE-2024-53113)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;kernel: ALSA: usb-audio: Fix potential out-of-bound accesses for Extigy and Mbox devices (CVE-2024-53197)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://access.redhat.com/errata/product/479/ver=/rhel---9/x86_64/RHSA-2025:2627&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://access.redhat.com/errata/product/479/ver=/rhel---9/x86_64/RHSA-2025:2627&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
